8!8i4864!4m3!8m2!3m1!1e1!6m1!1e1 Flushing Line platform]\n* [http://www.google.com/maps/@40.7556221,-73.9863938,3a,90y,36.18h,90.02t/data=!3m8!1e1!3m6!1s-lRXX0avVp0o%2FV4sajdk5cJI%2FAAAAAAAAKTA%2FV6MSEInabf4Z6f-ZJbvuucPFlDgjBsFmQCLIB!2e4!3e11!6s%2F%2Flh4.googleusercontent.com%2F-lRXX0avVp0o%2FV4sajdk5cJI%2FAAAAAAAAKTA%2FV6MSEInabf4Z6f-ZJbvuucPFlDgjBsFmQCLIB%2Fw203-h100-p-k-no%2F!7i9728!8i4864!4m3!8m2!3m1!1e1!6m1!1e1 Shuttle platforms]\n* [http://www.google.com/maps/@40.7543405,-73.9870878,3a,75y,231.28h,87.86t/data=!3m8!1e1!3m6!1s-jXgx3c1wMvs%2FV4nEGCbSNvI%2FAAAAAAAAKGY%2FdPu3iwrKEQgOkZUUgxtgPRJtLeHtGzIYQCLIB!2e4!3e11!6s%2F%2Flh6.googleusercontent.com%2F-jXgx3c1wMvs%2FV4nEGCbSNvI%2FAAAAAAAAKGY%2FdPu3iwrKEQgOkZUUgxtgPRJtLeHtGzIYQCLIB%2Fw203-h100-p-k-no%2F!7i9728!8i4864!4m3!8m2!3m1!1e1!6m1!1e1 BMT platforms]\n* [http://www.google.com/maps/@40.7558636,-73.9869289,3a,75y,93.2h,88.01t/data=!3m8!1e1!3m6!1s-pwQ6bXqFKVg%2FV42lgVAVAWI%2FAAAAAAAAK4o%2FxSi_koWUDRE8gt7XsmfwzLZ2Oc88KGtKwCLIB!2e4!3e11!6s%2F%2Flh5.googleusercontent.com%2F-pwQ6bXqFKVg%2FV42lgVAVAWI%2FAAAAAAAAK4o%2FxSi_koWUDRE8gt7XsmfwzLZ2Oc88KGtKwCLIB%2Fw203-h100-p-k-no%2F!7i9728!8i4864!4m3!8m2!3m1!1e1!6m1!1e1 Broadway - Seventh Avenue Line downtown platform]\n{{refend}}\n\n'''Other websites'''\n{{refbegin|30em}}\n* MTA's [[YouTube]] Web Page \u2013 [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WhxfZ0LabbE Advertising Initiatives 9/21/2010] on the 42nd Street (S) Shuttle. Retrieved September 22, 2010. (2:13 video clip)\n* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MelBbmdcSQQ NYCTA Subway Station Tour: 42nd Street\u2013Port Authority/Times Square]\n* Forgotten NY \u2013 [http://forgotten-ny.com/2006/01/the-original-28-part-2-a-look-at-the-artwork-from-the-nycs-first-28-stations-opened-october-27-1904/ Original 28 - NYC's First 28 Subway Stations]\n* The Subway Nut \u2013 [http://www.subwaynut.com/ct/times_sq_7/index.php Times Square\u201342nd Street (7) pictures]\n{{refend}}\n\n{{Clear}}\n\n{{NYCS stations navbox by service|l0=y|l1=y|l2=